Look what I got.
"Betty G."

777
00:38:56,599 --> 00:38:58,088
Yeah.
What is this?

778
00:38:58,168 --> 00:38:59,726
It's a doodle.
He doodled it!

779
00:39:00,135 --> 00:39:02,331
How do you know
he doodled it? How do
you know this is his?

780
00:39:02,438 --> 00:39:03,632
What do you mean,
how do I know it's his?

781
00:39:03,706 --> 00:39:05,231
I stole it out of
his overnight bag.

782
00:39:05,307 --> 00:39:07,070
