Strombel appears.
What?

916
00:47:10,458 --> 00:47:13,860
Yes, Strombel's in there!
I got a tremendous hand
from the audience.

917
00:47:13,963 --> 00:47:15,657
I wish
I could do it every night!

918
00:47:15,731 --> 00:47:16,822
What did he say?

919
00:47:17,032 --> 00:47:20,092
He gave me
the combination to a safe.

920
00:47:20,168 --> 00:47:22,193
What safe, I have no idea.

921
00:47:22,838 --> 00:47:24,271
I didn't see any safe.

922
00:47:25,106 --> 00:47:30,067
Well, did you
accomplish anything besides
maybe a possible pregnancy?

923
00:47:30,146 --> 00:47:31,510
