to rub somebody out
and not get caught.

1432
01:13:53,661 --> 01:13:55,958
Nobody wants
to get caught, Sidney.

1433
01:13:56,029 --> 01:13:57,019
Look,

1434
01:13:57,097 --> 01:14:00,931
he wants to get rid of
Elizabeth Gibson.
Betty Gibson. Betty Gibson.

1435
01:14:01,002 --> 01:14:03,162
So, there's
a series of murders

1436
01:14:03,237 --> 01:14:06,637
with a guy that's got
a real style. A Tarot card.

1437
01:14:06,707 --> 01:14:08,333
They said
he was a total maniac.

1438
01:14:08,408 --> 01:14:11,502
He buys a Tarot deck
and let's say he hides it.

1439
