just came to me.

1482
01:16:01,588 --> 01:16:02,715
I know I'm right.

1483
01:16:03,157 --> 01:16:05,056
She just won't listen to me.
She hates me.

1484
01:16:05,126 --> 01:16:06,319
Yeah. I...
You know,

1485
01:16:06,394 --> 01:16:08,988
sometimes, I got to say,
I worry about that girl.

1486
01:16:09,564 --> 01:16:12,555
