to get it for you.

1489
01:16:18,538 --> 01:16:20,802
You can only cheat death
so many times,

1490
01:16:21,274 --> 01:16:23,140
and I've used
every trick I know.

1491
01:16:23,743 --> 01:16:25,837
You look after her.
She's a decent kid.

1492
01:16:26,413 --> 01:16:30,077
And check
his Tarot deck.
See if a card's missing.

