entertain her clients here,
or not, I couldn't say.

1500
01:17:23,637 --> 01:17:25,537
(HUMMING)

1501
01:17:27,908 --> 01:17:32,902
(STUTTERING) Oh,
excuse me. I'm a reporter.

1502
01:17:33,346 --> 01:17:34,746
And I'm doing a story

1503
01:17:34,814 --> 01:17:37,716
(CLEARS THROAT)
About Elizabeth Gibson.

1504
01:17:37,784 --> 01:17:40,618
If there's any comments,
anything you know
about her that I...

1505
01:17:40,688 --> 01:17:45,351
What paper?
What paper are you from?
The Washington Post

1506
01:17:45,493 --> 01:17:48,894
I'm one of the top reporters
on the...

1507
01:17:48,962 --> 01:17:52,454
Did you see
All the President's Men?
I was the short guy.

1508
01:17:52,932 --> 01:17:54,923
(BOTH STUTTERING)

1509
01:17:55,002 --> 01:17:57,698
Why is an American paper
interested in this?

1510
01:17:57,771 --> 01:17:59,899
No, no, we are, we are.
We're doing a big story.

1511
01:17:59,974 --> 01:18:03,000
The Travel and Leisure section
is doing a big spread

1512
01:18:03,077 --> 01:18:05,045
on places
to avoid like the plague.

1513
01:18:05,112 --> 01:18:07,444
And so, I'm...

1514
01:18:07,782 --> 01:18:12,047
I'll make it
very worth your while,
you know and...

1515
01:18:12,118 --> 01:18:14,609
All right, all right,
all right. I knew
Betty Gibson.

1516
01:18:15,288 --> 01:18:17,449
Mmm-hmm,
and she was very tough.

1517
01:18:17,891 --> 01:18:20,326
But I don't think
that she deserved to die.

1518
01:18:20,728 --> 01:18:22,524
Did you say Betty Gibson?

1519
01:18:23,930 --> 01:18:27,297
Everyone called her Betty.
That was her name.

1520
01:18:27,768 --> 01:18:32,261
Really?
And did you know any
of her clients at all?

1521
01:18:32,439 --> 01:18:34,100
(SCOFFS)

