1544
01:19:42,176 --> 01:19:43,369
You could have come.

1545
01:19:43,911 --> 01:19:48,371
That's okay. She gave me
this number to call.
May I speak with her?

1546
01:19:48,448 --> 01:19:49,541
Yes, one second.

1547
01:19:57,257 --> 01:19:58,384
Hi, Sidney.

1548
01:19:58,458 --> 01:20:02,087
Listen,
I got a treasure trove
of information here.

1549
01:20:02,229 --> 01:20:04,993
I just was snooping with...

1550
01:20:05,666 --> 01:20:07,759
On Elizabeth Gibson.

1551
01:20:08,034 --> 01:20:10,525
She's called Betty. Betty!
She's called Betty.

1552
01:20:10,738 --> 01:20:14,195
