Yes, yes.

1574
01:21:21,708 --> 01:21:24,371
You know, I love Sidney,
I really do,

1575
01:21:24,444 --> 01:21:26,935
but he's just...
He's got a part missing,
you know, he's crazy!

1576
01:21:27,014 --> 01:21:28,275
Yes, really?
Mmm-hmm.

1577
01:21:28,349 --> 01:21:29,372
